fields.description:
Muweku Suppliers Limited was formed in 2021 and incorporated in 2022 as a renowned supplier in
Zambia. Our primary objective is to supply Mechanical, Electrical materials and components, Stationery
and Cleaning Materials to various vendors. Muweku Suppliers Ltd key activities comprise the Mechanical
and Electrical Materials, Stationery, Cleaning Materials, and general supplies. These include; bearings,
bolts and nuts, filters, round bars, batteries, power transformers and voltage converters, electric cables, etc.
and general dealings.
Muweku aims at building a strong and healthy market trust through a simple principle that we follow: Earn
Trust with Business, and focuses on providing support and services to all major industries, contractors and
traders in the region.
Muweku Office employs qualified and innovative individuals who have the necessary skills and years of
experience to respond to todays, challenges and requirements. Exceeding client satisfaction motivates
Muweku Office team of staff.

(E-Trac) Zambia – Fleet Management & GPS Tracking Solutions

(E-Trac) Zambia is a leading fleet management and GPS tracking solutions provider, offering an advanced TELEMATICS PLATFORM. Our platform empowers you to monitor your valuable assets and vehicles from any computer or mobile device—ensuring safety, efficiency, and real-time tracking.

At E-Trac Zambia, we are committed to inventing, developing, and delivering the best GPS/GNSS solutions in the industry. Our technology creates a secure and monitored environment, allowing you to locate, sense, and analyze everything valuable to you and your business—anytime, anywhere.

Comprehensive Fleet & Asset Tracking Solutions

Our advanced fleet monitoring and management systems can be applied to various tracking scenarios, including:

  • ✅ Trucks & Trailers
  • ✅ Boats & Vans
  • ✅ Cars & Bikes
  • ✅ Heavy Equipment & Inventory

Real-Time Fleet Monitoring & Management

With our real-time fleet monitoring and management system, you can:

  • ✔️ Coordinate and control your company's staff and vehicles
  • ✔️ Optimize journeys to save time and reduce costs
  • ✔️ Enhance productivity by streamlining your operations

Why Choose E-Trac Zambia?

At E-Trac Zambia, we believe in delivering 110% effort. By closing the loop on fleet management and leveraging cutting-edge GPS technology, we help businesses grow, improve operational efficiency, and increase productivity.

As our Managing Director puts it:

"Efficiencies will come from proactively transforming how we do business."

Join us today and experience next-level fleet management and GPS tracking solutions!
